title: Laracasts - Feb. 24 - Customer Analysis With Trak.io
description:
Customer Analysis With Trak.io

Trak.io is a new service, in Beta, that provides incredible insight into the actions of your customers/users. In this lesson, we'll integrate it with this very site - in real-time!

Please note that we'll be using the official JavaScript library to send our events to Trak.io. If you'd instead prefer to tackle this directly with PHP, you could first register various custom events in your Laravel app, and then reference this package within your event handler(s) to perform your API requests.
